column2: Wet spring.  Lake level returning to low to normal.  Clear skies.  Water clear.
Partly cloudy skies.  Water color blue to green.
Clear skies- algae bloom started.  85 F air temp.  Calm to light wind.
Sunny. Water filled with 6 to 8 foot clumps of floating aquatic vegetation.
Sunny to slightly cloudy. Sunny to slightly cloudy.
Larry Hart- and Kris Larson also checked water quality on this date.
Al Spatenka- Craig Nackeride- Dave Blumer and Larry Hart
Ice out one week prior on 04/28/14
